        <p class="mt-4 text-xs text-white/50">
          Full walkthrough: <a href="/learn/verify-license" class="underline underline-offset-2">step-by-step licence verification guide</a> · <a href="https://spca.org.sg/campaigns/animal-smuggling/" class="underline underline-offset-2">SPCA on animal smuggling</a>
        </p>
